Hello Richard
A lot of the evp recordings I have done seem to be out of context, 
however I have received some
direct responses. Some sound human, some sound prerecorded and some 
sound robotic.
All in all - extremely interesting.
I record in a variety of places and usually always carry my RCA Digital 
recorder with me at all times and
it leads to some puzzling results. But that is what makes this so fun, 
you never know what you will get.

Stephen ..
http://evpresearch.redirectme.net


